No. 11-6460. Rosie Washington, et vir, Petitioners v. Louisiana, et al. 565 U.S. 1056, 132 S. Ct. 797,

181 L. Ed. 2d 478,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8536. November 28, 2011.

Motion of petitioners for leave to proceed in forma pauperis *479denied. Petitioners are allowed until December 19, 2011, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.

Same case below, 425 Fed. Appx. 330.
